templates.name: Search phrase 14
templates.cypher:
MATCH (n {label: $molecule})<-[r1:catalyzedBy|product|substrate]-(r)-[r2:isPartOf]->(p)
RETURN n, r, r1, p, r2

templates.name: Get metabolic pathways that involve the enzyme
templates.cypher:
MATCH (n {label: $enzyme})<-[r1:catalyzedBy]-(r)-[r2:isPartOf]->(p)
RETURN n, r, r1, p, r2

templates.name: Search phrase 11
templates.cypher:
MATCH (n {id: $workflow})-[r:uses]->(eq)-[:IS_SUBCLASS_OF*..4]->({id: "Equation"})
OPTIONAL MATCH (n)-[r:uses]->(rule)-[:IS_SUBCLASS_OF*..4]->({id: "Rule"})
RETURN eq, rule

templates.name: Get 'submodels' used by the workflow
templates.cypher:
MATCH (n {id: $workflow})-[r1:uses]->(m)
WHERE (m)-[:IS_SUBCLASS_OF*..]->({id: "Model Brain Component"}) OR (m)-[:IS_SUBCLASS_OF*..]->({id: "Model Brain Activity"})
WITH n, r1, m
OPTIONAL MATCH (m)<-[r2:generates]-(subworkflow)
WITH n, r1, m, r2, subworkflow
OPTIONAL MATCH (used)<-[r3:uses]-(subworkflow)
RETURN n, r1, m, subworkflow, r2, used, r3

templates.name: Search phrase 8
templates.cypher:
MATCH path=((n {id: "Biological Brain Component"})<-[:IS_SUBCLASS_OF*]-(nn)), (nn)-[r:componentType]->(t), (n)-[r0:componentType]->(tt)
RETURN n, path, nn, r, t, r0, tt

templates.name: Search phrase 7
templates.cypher:
MATCH (n {id: "Biological Brain Component"})<-[:IS_SUBCLASS_OF*..]-(c)-[r:isPartOf]->(m)
RETURN c, m, r

templates.name: Search phrase 6
templates.cypher:
MATCH (n {id: "Biological Brain Component"}), path=((n)<-[:IS_SUBCLASS_OF*..]-(m))
RETURN n, m, path

templates.name: Get detailed list of parameters for the workflow
templates.cypher:
MATCH (n {id: $workflow})-[r:hasParameter]->(t)
WITH n, r, t
OPTIONAL MATCH path=((t)<-[:IS_SUBCLASS_OF*]-(a))
RETURN n, r, t, path, a

templates.name: Get detailed list of target features for the workflow
templates.cypher:
MATCH (n {id: $workflow})-[r:hasTarget]->(t), path=((t)<-[:IS_SUBCLASS_OF*..]-(a))
WITH n, r, t, path, a
OPTIONAL MATCH (a)-[sr:stimulusType]->(s), (a)-[cr:compartment]->(c)
RETURN n, r, t, path, a, s, sr, cr, c

templates.name: Get details on feature extraction for the workflow
templates.cypher:
MATCH (n {id: $workflow})-[r1:hasTarget]->(t)<-[g:generates]-(fe_workflow)-[:IS_SUBCLASS_OF*..]->({id: "Feature Extraction Workflow"}), (fe_workflow)-[u:uses]->(d)
RETURN n, t, r1, fe_workflow, g, d, u

templates.name: Get dataset classes needed to run the workflow
templates.cypher:
MATCH (n {id: $workflow})-[r:uses]->(d)-[:IS_SUBCLASS_OF*..4]->({id: "Dataset"})
OPTIONAL MATCH (n)-[rt:hasTarget]->(t)<-[:generates]-()-[:uses]->(td)
RETURN d, td

templates.name: Get all ontology classes and IS_A relations
How to build a specific model type
templates.cypher:
MATCH (model_type {id: $MODEL_TYPE})<-[r1:generates]-(workflow)-[:IS_SUBCLASS_OF*]->({id: "Workflow"})
WITH model_type, r1, workflow
OPTIONAL MATCH (workflow)-[r2:hasTarget]->(target)
WITH model_type, r1, workflow, r2, target
OPTIONAL MATCH (workflow)-[r3:uses]->(used)
WITH model_type, r1, workflow, r2, target, r3, used
OPTIONAL MATCH (workflow)-[r4:hasParameter]->(parameter)
RETURN model_type, r1, workflow, r2, target, r3, used, r4, parameter

params.name: $MODEL_TYPE
params.cypher:
MATCH (m)
WHERE ({id: "Model Brain Component"})<-[:IS_SUBCLASS_OF*..]-(m) OR ({id: "Model Brain Activity"})<-[:IS_SUBCLASS_OF*..]-(m) 
RETURN m.id
